snippet.title: SMALL CUTE DRAGONS will make sure that YOU'LL LAUGH - The FUNNIEST LIZARD VIDEOS
snippet.description:
Lizards are very interesting, cute and hilarious animals! Just like cats and dogs, lizards never fail to make us laugh super hard! These funny lizard videos are the hardest try not to laugh challenge! Just look how all these geckos, chameleons, bearded dragons,... behave, play, fail, annoy, steal, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
